sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin
    participant CreateElection
    participant DeployAPI
    participant SupabaseDB
    participant Blockchain
    
    Admin->>CreateElection: Fill election form
    CreateElection->>CreateElection: Validate form data
    CreateElection->>DeployAPI: POST /api/deploy
    DeployAPI->>DeployAPI: Authenticate user
    DeployAPI->>DeployAPI: Validate positions/candidates
    DeployAPI->>Blockchain: Deploy contract (ContractFactory)
    Blockchain-->>DeployAPI: Contract address + txHash
    DeployAPI->>SupabaseDB: Generate unique 7-digit code
    DeployAPI->>SupabaseDB: Insert election record
    SupabaseDB-->>DeployAPI: Election ID
    DeployAPI-->>CreateElection: {electionId, contractAddress, txHash}
    CreateElection->>Admin: Show success dialog
    Admin->>CreateElection: Continue
    CreateElection->>Admin: Navigate to election view

